Query: The Query string to get the data to be stored in this object, for example: select * from Yggdrasil where Dataset.DataType = 'something'
Schema: The data Schema, will define form fields and segments
Parameters: The data entry process, sort by timestamp of input event
Data: The State of the form, the actual data object
Checksum: The Data checksum string, containing MD5 checksum of the [Dataset > Data] as string
DataType: Data classification string, for example: Transaksi Penjualan
ExternalResource: This is an array containing the external resource, for example image files, PDF files, Spreadsheet files, etc
ProcessingParameters: This is the Processing Parameters object, containing the Next Process Locking , Signage, etc
